  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施组件的依赖流转图。起点是Redis缓存层，它要先连到Etcd集群做服务发现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，Redis缓存指向Etcd集群。那Etcd之后流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Etcd配置好了之后，流量要走到负载均衡器。然后这里有个关键判断点——负载均衡器要检查Redis缓存的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上负载均衡器，然后连到一个判断节点来检查Redis状态。这个判断用菱形表示对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，菱形判断。如果Redis可用，走Yes分支到Ingress控制器；如果不可用，走No分支回退到Etcd集群重新拉取配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。Ingress控制器和回退的Etcd集群都接上了。那Ingress控制器之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Ingress控制器和刚才回退到Etcd的那条路，最终都要汇聚到第二个判断点——再次检查负载均衡器的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Ingress控制器和Etcd集群是并行汇入同一个负载均衡器判断节点，对吗？不是先后关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，两条线汇合。然后这个负载均衡器判断如果为Yes，要回到最开始的Etcd集群形成闭环；如果No，就结束到Etcd集群做降级处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，您刚才说Yes回到Etcd集群，但之前回退分支也指向Etcd。我需要区分一下——闭环回到的是B节点那个Etcd，还是新的终点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好问题。Yes分支回到B节点，就是最开始那个Etcd集群，形成循环；No分支指向H节点，是一个独立的Etcd降级节点，虽然类型一样但是不同实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，Yes闭环回B，No到新的H节点。我调整一下连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼整体：Redis→Etcd→负载均衡器→判断Redis→Yes到Ingress/No回Etcd→汇合判断负载均衡器→Yes闭环/No降级。逻辑通吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "通的。我注意到第一个判断节点的标签是Yes/No，第二个也是Yes/No，需要标注更明确吗？比如\"缓存可用\"这种？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持Yes/No就行，简洁。但两个判断节点的含义不同：D节点是检查Redis状态，G节点是检查负载均衡器健康度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。两个菱形判断，D接Redis检查，G接负载均衡器检查，所有分支和闭环都画好了。您验收一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
